I&#x27;m not sure what your complaint is.<p><pre><code>    import Control.Monad (forM_)

    fizzbuzz i | i `mod` 3 == 0 = Left &quot;fizz&quot;
               | i `mod` 5 == 0 = Left &quot;buzz&quot;
               | otherwise      = Right i

    main = forM_ [1..100] (\i -> either putStrLn print (fizzbuzz i))</code></pre>
